  panelCanvasGroup: {fileID: 452337289}
  titleText: {fileID: 1001613000}
  title: HOW TO PLAY
  bodyText: {fileID: 716476777}
  body: 'Choose one block in each room.


    Press E at the terminal to check the
    condition.


    The door opens only when the statement is TRUE.


    The rooms
    get harder: first simple if checks, then OR, then AND + OR combinations.


    If
    a condition fails, pick another block and try again.'
  toggleKey: 282
